{
  "stem": "22883.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that moment I realized, because we heard there was a group of hoodlums from this very far right organization, and they came to the city just to beat the Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because I had this uniform-- this uniform was a very khaki uniform, OK, and very similar to the uniforms of Jewish organizations, which was of course they-- later on, they became the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in Poland, they had young Jewish boys, they were members of the organization, paramilitary organization, and were going to the woods, and they were having some military exercises.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In 1939 and '38 and 1937.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- were wearing khaki uniforms which are very similar to that uniform what I was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this policeman, a Polish policeman, there were no Jews in the police.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This policeman, seeing me in this uniform and, of course, as usually, my face was with this long nose and so and so on, so he assumed that I am Jew.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was warning me not to go, because I could get hurt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because of those-- those hoodlums.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you see, this is one positive indication that not Polish-- and policemen were not educated people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Ordinary people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had some kind of compassion, or something like that, and he-- he wanted to avoid having somebody hurt by-- by those hoodlums.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's one of-- illustration giving you maybe some answer to how the Polish population was toward Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
